Sigrid escapes as raven, lays egg for 1944 voter

IV. CONTAMINATION AS TOTAL SYSTEM
Everything is poisoned. You cannot use the master's tools without being poisoned by them.
Contamination Layers
Food: Hákarl 77 days too early (neurotoxin), empty sea, hidden bread while family starves
Ritual Materials: Industrial rope with veins, brass military buttons growing from fish skulls
Land: Trawler oil sheens, 50-meter radius of poisoned ground, polynya contaminated
Gods Themselves: Griðungur has V-notch marks and harpoons, Jörmungandr IS trawler
Language: Danish overwrites Icelandic, counting in Danish drops temperature, creates 3mm frost per word
Time: Non-linear, all moments simultaneous, temporal sickness
Visual Contamination Progress

Shot 1-20: Environmental only (tar in beams, oil in water)
Shot 30: Black fibers appear in hákarl meat
Shot 50: Wool emerges from Guðrún's wrists
Shot 78-80: Magnús finally contaminated when challenging trawler

V. THE MYTHOLOGICAL FUSION
The Four Landvættir (Accidentally Summoned, Contaminated)
BERGRISI (Mountain Giant/South): The house IS the giant's body. Family lives inside its stomach. Breathing 12/minute (anxiety), slowing to 11 (prey resignation), accelerating to 25 (panic), finally 3 dying breaths. Seven warm spots on floor = organs. Pink flesh visible beneath walls. Protects Sigrid with warm air bubble.
GRIÐUNGUR (Bull/West): Emerges from polynya with industrial materials fused - harpoons through skull, brass fixtures growing from flesh, rope with veins around neck. V-notch in ear (colonial marking). Appears at threshold without explanation.
JÖRMUNGANDR (Dragon-Serpent/East): British steam trawler IS the World Serpent wearing modernity. Yellow electric lights as eyes. Warm yellow electric light inside wheelhouse. Creates ouroboros at climax triggering Ragnarök. Horn progression 70Hz to 85Hz. Speaks: "VAK" "RÍS" "NÚ".
GAMMUR (Eagle-Raven/North): Ancient witness in three 12-second monolithic holds. Eye shows all futures simultaneously. Transforms Sigrid through blessing not violence. Ravens multiply: 1→3→7→70→hundreds→millions forming walls.
Norse Mythology Layers

Huginn & Muninn: When camera fragments, it's these two separating
The Nornir: Three rope cuttings - trawler cuts line (past), Guðrún cuts wool (present), Sigrid cuts tilberi (future)
HAMR Concept: Shape/form that can be shed - carved in floor (ancient), written in dust (present), painted in blood (future)
Ragnarök Triggers: Eternal winter, sun disappearing, serpent releasing tail

VI. THE WITNESS MECHANISM
Seven Layers of Watching

Cosmic: Aurora withdrawing, ravens circling
Divine: Bergrisi choosing, landvættir observing
Imperial: Danish administration counting, British trawler surveilling
Domestic: Magnús watching family, family watching each other
Structural: House breathing with occupants
Documentary: Camera as Iceland watching itself die
Audience: We are complicit witnesses, eventual tourists

The Surveillance Web (Core Device)

Sigrid watches everyone (survival)
Guðrún watches Magnús (fear)
Magnús watches for betrayal
Children watch without understanding
United only when watching shark meat

Camera as Character
The camera IS Iceland itself, documenting its own colonization. Trembles at 3Hz (inherited colonial disease). Accumulates frost throughout (0% = 1262 lost independence, 100% = 1944 independence). Must document to die, must die to transform. Fragments into seven views at climax.
Sigrid as Designated Witness
Only one who escapes to testify. Maintains 11-foot distance (witness space). Breathes at human rate while others synchronize to prey rate. Protected by Bergrisi's recognition. Transforms to raven (memory/witness) not sheep (commodity). Lays egg in 1920 containing 1944 voter.
